<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>

<body>


    <div class="header-banner">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="banner">
                <div class="indent">
                    <h2 class="indent-left margin-bot">Plan the Easy Trip</h2>
                    <div class="banner-left">
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/glass.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Restaurants</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/flight.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Flights</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/group.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Things to do</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/key.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Vacation Rents</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="header_bottom_right_images">

                        <div class="slider" style="width:650px;height:375px;">
                            <ul class="rslides" id="slider1">
                                @foreach (var x in Model)
                                {
                                    <li><img src="@x.BlogImage" style="width:650px; height:375px;" alt=""></li>
                                }

                                @*<li><img src="~/web/images/img1.jpg" alt=""></li>
                                    <li><img src="~/web/images/img2.jpg" alt=""></li>
                                    <li><img src="~/web/images/img3.jpg" alt=""></li>
                                    <li><img src="~/web/images/img4.jpg" alt=""></li>*@
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clear"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class"content">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="con-top">
                    <h3>Welcome to our Travel Company!</h3>
                    <p>
                        What We Believe
                        Everyone at Welcome to Travel, is a traveller at heart and the reason why we travel is to:

                        Have new experiences that will broaden our horizons.

                        Explore new places, as it sparks creativity.

                        To connect with people from around the world with similar values.

                        You will be amazed at how one shared experience can create a lifelong friendship.

                        All it takes is to start…Take that first step… But we know it can be overwhelming and daunting.

                        This is exactly why we set up Welcome to Travel, so you can meet like minded people and discover places that you have only ever dreamed of.

                        This is the start of your travel story, so let us share ours with you.
                    </p>
                </div>
                @Html.Action("Partial1","Default")
                <div class="grids">
                    <div class="box1">
                        @Html.Action("Partial3", "Default")
                        @Html.Action("Partial4", "Default")

                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
